OL,3,C'I'd love to throw Sir Sadiq Khan into
OL,4,Ca black hole', says Tory election rival
OL,6,FLondon Assembly Tory Susan Hall - who
OL,7,Fstood against Khan in last year's
OL,8,Felection - told the mayor his
OL,9,Fpredecessor Boris Johnson would be
OL,10,F"doing a better job than you are" if
OL,11,Fhe was still in office.
OL,13,FNeil Garratt, leader of the London
OL,14,FAssembly Conservatives, accused Khan
OL,15,Fof ranting during a row over council
OL,16,Ftax bills while Khan accused Garratt
OL,17,Fof being abusive.
