OL,3,C'I'd love to throw Sir Sadiq Khan into
OL,4,Ca black hole', says Tory election rival
OL,6,FThe political point scoring carried on
OL,7,Fthroughout the hour-long meeting of
OL,8,Fthe assembly's Budget and Performance
OL,9,FCommittee, chaired by Garratt.
OL,11,FHall began her attack by reminding
OL,12,FKhan of his election sales pitch about
OL,13,Fthe benefits of a Labour mayor with a
OL,14,FLabour government.
OL,16,F"You told us if we had a Labour
OL,17,Fgovernment, everything in the world
OL,18,Fwould be rosy and to have less police
OL,19,Fofficers is not what Londoners want,
OL,20,Fis it?" asked Hall.
