OL,3,C'I'd love to throw Sir Sadiq Khan into
OL,4,Ca black hole', says Tory election rival
OL,6,FKhan replied: "This year we will have
OL,7,Fmore money going to the Met police
OL,8,Fservice than any year since the Met
OL,9,Fpolice was founded 196 years ago
OL,10,Fthanks to the Labour government's
OL,11,Fgenerosity".
OL,13,FPolice commissioner Sir Mark Rowley
OL,14,Fsaid on Tuesday the force was facing
OL,15,F"tough choice" cuts because of a #260m
OL,16,Ffunding shortfall.
OL,18,FHall told Khan his decision to allow
OL,19,Fjust 60 minutes for questions was a
OL,20,F"damned disgrace".
