OL,3,C'I'd love to throw Sir Sadiq Khan into
OL,4,Ca black hole', says Tory election rival
OL,6,FThe mayor declined to say which police
OL,7,Funits would be cut because it was
OL,8,F"unwise to give a running commentary
OL,9,Fon what choices the Commissioner is
OL,10,Fgoing to make."
OL,12,FHall hit back: "I can only imagine you
OL,13,Fdon't know, which is shocking bearing
OL,14,Fin mind you are the police and crime
OL,15,Fcommissioner"
OL,17,FKhan told the meeting the Metropolitan
OL,18,FPolice Service was #500m worse off
OL,19,Fbecause of funding decisions made by
OL,20,FJohnson, including council tax cuts.
